<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 22:06:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列南部城市市长致内塔尼亚胡：允许高中生进行枪械训练</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/mayor-of-southern-israeli-city-to-netanyahu-allow-firearm-training-for-high-schoolers/0000018c-ef2f-d7da-adac-ff3f2eb30000</link><description>加特镇市长阿维拉姆·达哈里 (Aviram Dahari) 写道，该市“希望在以色列人民为家园而战的日子里成为实施这项非常基础的训练的先锋”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 19:23:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/mayor-of-southern-israeli-city-to-netanyahu-allow-firearm-training-for-high-schoolers/0000018c-ef2f-d7da-adac-ff3f2eb30000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯：针对以色列的种族灭绝指控“毫无根据”；必须允许巴勒斯坦人返回加沙北部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/blinken-genocide-charge-against-israel-meritless-palestinians-must-be-allowed-return/0000018c-ef8f-da6b-abdd-ffcf48d60000</link><description>布林肯在周二与以色列官员会面后的新闻发布会上发表了讲话。与此同时，美国和以色列在加沙的未来问题上仍存在严重分歧 — — 特别是关于重振巴勒斯坦权力机构的潜在作用，布林肯将于周三会见该权力机构</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 19:20:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/blinken-genocide-charge-against-israel-meritless-palestinians-must-be-allowed-return/0000018c-ef8f-da6b-abdd-ffcf48d60000</guid></item><item><title>“当我们无法同情巴勒斯坦人时，我们怎么能指望其他人同情我们呢？”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-01-09/ty-article-podcast/.premium/how-can-we-expect-others-to-empathize-with-us-if-we-fail-to-empathize-with-palestinians/0000018c-ef0a-d7da-adac-ff1b816a0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 17:17:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-01-09/ty-article-podcast/.premium/how-can-we-expect-others-to-empathize-with-us-if-we-fail-to-empathize-with-palestinians/0000018c-ef0a-d7da-adac-ff1b816a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质家属试图阻止对加沙的援助，在布林肯面前示威</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-attempt-to-block-aid-into-gaza-protest-in-front-of-blinken/0000018c-eea8-d7da-adac-feb940080000</link><description>“我们的政府没有履行其使命。我们需要美国的紧急帮助，我们需要人质现在活着回家。我们为什么现在在这里？我们的亲人被关押在加沙 100 天后，”拥有美国和以色列双重国籍的齐皮·海托夫斯基 (Tsipi Haitovski) 在抗议活动中说道</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 16:07:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-attempt-to-block-aid-into-gaza-protest-in-front-of-blinken/0000018c-eea8-d7da-adac-feb940080000</guid></item><item><title>以色列声称在数十次跨境袭击中杀死了真主党无人机负责人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-hezbollah-exchange-dozens-of-cross-border-strikes-on-tuesday/0000018c-ee36-d7da-adac-fe375bbb0000</link><description>真主党从黎巴嫩向以色列国防军基地发射爆炸性无人机，而以色列对黎巴嫩南部的袭击导致三名真主党战士死亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 15:03:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-hezbollah-exchange-dozens-of-cross-border-strikes-on-tuesday/0000018c-ee36-d7da-adac-fe375bbb0000</guid></item><item><title>接地：以色列人目前不属于世界</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/grounded-israelis-are-currently-not-part-of-the-world/0000018c-ee39-d0b4-a7ce-ff7b9e460000</link><description>特拉维夫的本古里安国际机场空无一人，外国航空公司没有航班飞往这里，以色列人只是梦想着度假</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 13:39:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/grounded-israelis-are-currently-not-part-of-the-world/0000018c-ee39-d0b4-a7ce-ff7b9e460000</guid></item><item><title>“当以色列与哈马斯战争爆发时，Apple TV 要求停止编写剧本”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/television/2024-01-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-the-israel-hamas-war-broke-out-apple-tv-asked-to-stop-writing-the-script/0000018c-ee37-d7da-adac-fe37d7080000</link><description>近年来，以色列电视剧越来越受欢迎，广播公司与外国同行达成了协议。但自从战争爆发以来，合作就被冻结了。一位生产商警告说：“我们很可能会变得像俄罗斯一样”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 13:24:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/television/2024-01-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-the-israel-hamas-war-broke-out-apple-tv-asked-to-stop-writing-the-script/0000018c-ee37-d7da-adac-fe37d7080000</guid></item><item><title>新调查显示，一名荷兰国民在 2008 年破坏了伊朗核计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/a-dutch-national-sabotaged-irans-nuclear-program-in-2008-new-investigation-reveals/0000018c-ee18-d0b4-a7ce-ff7bc9ec0000</link><description>Stuxnet 是一种导致伊朗核计划瘫痪的恶意软件，据信是由一​​名伊朗工程师释放的。一份具有里程碑意义的新报告显示这是一名荷兰国民——与摩萨德和中央情报局合作</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 12:51:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/a-dutch-national-sabotaged-irans-nuclear-program-in-2008-new-investigation-reveals/0000018c-ee18-d0b4-a7ce-ff7bc9ec0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯进入新的战争阶段，但仍没有加沙战后计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/phase-three-of-the-war-has-begun-and-israel-still-doesnt-have-a-postwar-plan-for-gaza/0000018c-ed7b-d89f-adcc-fffbd7e10000</link><description>美国和埃及都就加沙未来政府的样子提出了合理的想法，但以色列似乎拒绝讨论“以色列持续安全控制”之外的未来。战争进入第四个月，未来与战争开始时一样悬而未决</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 12:48:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/phase-three-of-the-war-has-begun-and-israel-still-doesnt-have-a-postwar-plan-for-gaza/0000018c-ed7b-d89f-adcc-fffbd7e10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会释放人质：我看到他们伤害被囚禁的妇女</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/released-israeli-hostage-to-knesset-i-saw-them-harming-women-in-captivity/0000018c-edd3-d0b4-a7ce-fff308f50000</link><description>“我们确切地知道他们在 10 月 7 日做了什么。如果他们有能力做到这一点——他们在 90 天内能做什么？” 19 岁丹妮拉·吉尔博亚 (Daniela Gilboa) 在加沙地带被哈马斯扣为人质，她的母亲说道</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 12:33:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/released-israeli-hostage-to-knesset-i-saw-them-harming-women-in-captivity/0000018c-edd3-d0b4-a7ce-fff308f50000</guid></item><item><title>70名以色列议员签署动议，驱逐支持国际法院种族灭绝指控的MK</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/70-israeli-lawmakers-sign-motion-to-expel-mk-for-supporting-icj-genocide-charges/0000018c-ed46-d7fa-a9be-fd67f72f0000</link><description>奥弗·卡西夫议员表示，“虽然那些明确呼吁用火或原子弹摧毁加沙的人坐在内阁会议桌前，但我面临着因‘支持针对以色列的武装斗争’未经证实的指控而被驱逐”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 10:05:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/70-israeli-lawmakers-sign-motion-to-expel-mk-for-supporting-icj-genocide-charges/0000018c-ed46-d7fa-a9be-fd67f72f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了周一在加沙战斗中丧生的九名以色列士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/idf-releases-names-of-four-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat/0000018c-ed4a-d7fa-a9be-fd6fa5960000</link><description>被杀的士兵是加夫里尔·布鲁姆（Gavriel Bloom），27 岁；大卫·施瓦茨，26；亚基尔·赫克斯特，26 岁；罗伊塔尔，19 岁；罗伊·亚伯拉罕·迈蒙，24 岁；阿齐瓦·亚辛斯基，35 岁；阿米特·摩西·沙哈尔，25 岁​​；丹尼斯·克罗赫马洛夫·韦克斯勒，32 岁；罗恩·埃弗里米，26 岁</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 09:29:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/idf-releases-names-of-four-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat/0000018c-ed4a-d7fa-a9be-fd6fa5960000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯裔以色列男子在以色列北部的家中被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-man-fatally-shot-in-his-home-in-northern-israel/0000018c-ed23-db55-a39e-ffb719040000</link><description>受害者没有犯罪记录，是以色列阿拉伯社区自 2024 年初以来的第三名凶杀案受害者。警方怀疑枪击动机与他在灰色市场获得的一笔贷款有关</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 08:01:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-man-fatally-shot-in-his-home-in-northern-israel/0000018c-ed23-db55-a39e-ffb719040000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯提醒以色列，加沙战争尚未结束，北方紧张局势加剧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/hamas-reminds-israel-that-the-gaza-war-is-not-over-as-tensions-rise-in-the-north/0000018c-eb05-d0e9-a3de-ffcd85040000</link><description>以色列用英语和希伯来语窃窃私语，加沙战争的第三阶段已经开始——从大规模空中和地面战斗转向有针对性的行动 ■ 拉德万部队负责人被暗杀是向真主党高级官员发出的信息■ 布林肯来这里是为了推动加沙和黎巴嫩的解决方案，但他在耶路撒冷的东道主对此表示怀疑</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 04:00:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/hamas-reminds-israel-that-the-gaza-war-is-not-over-as-tensions-rise-in-the-north/0000018c-eb05-d0e9-a3de-ffcd85040000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯：内塔尼亚胡否认加沙转移是以色列的政策；以色列国防军调查坦克爆炸导致士兵死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article-live/blinken-to-meet-israeli-leaders-hezbollah-confirms-death-of-senior-commander-in-lebanon/0000018c-ec30-df6f-ad8e-ec77ad540000</link><description>以色列声称对暗杀真主党无人机部队负责人 ■ 周一，九名以色列国防军士兵在加沙地带丧生 ■ 以色列国防军对造成六名士兵死亡的坦克火灾展开调查 ■ 布林肯在第四次战时访问中会见以色列领导人，表示以色列必须允许巴勒斯坦人返回加沙北部的家园 ■ 布林肯称对以色列的种族灭绝指控“毫无根据”，英国首相卡梅伦表示，他“担心”以色列可能违反了国际法 ■ 以色列外交部否认参与将加沙居民迁出加沙地带的计划</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 03:18:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article-live/blinken-to-meet-israeli-leaders-hezbollah-confirms-death-of-senior-commander-in-lebanon/0000018c-ec30-df6f-ad8e-ec77ad540000</guid></item><item><title>以色列 Netflix 热门节目《Fauda》的明星在加沙战斗中受重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/star-of-hit-israeli-netflix-show-fauda-severely-wounded-in-gaza-combat/0000018c-eb27-da45-abbf-eb6795690000</link><description>伊丹·阿梅迪是以色列国防军工程兵的预备役士兵，10月7日后被征召入伍，战争期间随部队在加沙执行任务</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 22:40:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/star-of-hit-israeli-netflix-show-fauda-severely-wounded-in-gaza-combat/0000018c-eb27-da45-abbf-eb6795690000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日三个月后，联合国向以色列派遣性暴力代表</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/three-months-after-october-7-un-sending-sexual-violence-representative-to-israel/0000018c-eb14-da45-abbf-eb741aa90000</link><description>毛里求斯律师普拉米拉·帕滕是首位为此目的派往以色列的联合国官员，应外交部邀请并被授予调查权</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 22:14:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-09/ty-article/.premium/three-months-after-october-7-un-sending-sexual-violence-representative-to-israel/0000018c-eb14-da45-abbf-eb741aa90000</guid></item><item><title>巴拉克的任命是以色列在国际法院的防弹衣</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/baraks-appointment-is-a-flak-jacket-for-israel-at-the-international-court-of-justice/0000018c-eaa5-df6f-ad8e-eae78ea10000</link><description>这位前首席大法官的国际地位和独特的历史使他成为针对以色列种族灭绝指控案件的正确任命。但重要的是，他所代表的价值观不仅在外部得到体现，而且在国内得到真正的接受</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 21:56:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/baraks-appointment-is-a-flak-jacket-for-israel-at-the-international-court-of-justice/0000018c-eaa5-df6f-ad8e-eae78ea10000</guid></item><item><title>阿米猜·奇克利 (Amichai Chikli) 辞去以色列社会平等部长职务，将继续担任侨民事务部长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/chikli-to-resign-as-israels-social-equality-minister-remains-diaspora-affairs-minister/0000018c-ea6d-d0e9-a3de-feed5e7a0000</link><description>该部长通知以色列总理，他将辞去职务，因为内塔尼亚胡政府因在战争期间维持 31 个办公室而浪费资源而受到公众批评</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 19:53:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-08/ty-article/.premium/chikli-to-resign-as-israels-social-equality-minister-remains-diaspora-affairs-minister/0000018c-ea6d-d0e9-a3de-feed5e7a0000</guid></item><item><title>“现实已经暂停”：来自以色列加沙前线和黎巴嫩边境的报道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-08/ty-article/.highlight/reality-has-been-suspended-reporting-from-israels-front-lines-in-gaza-and-the-north/0000018c-e998-d249-a1ce-efddef3e0000</link><description>国土报记者安谢尔·普费弗（Anshel Pfeffer）和巴尔·佩莱格（Bar Peleg）最近加入了驻加沙城和黎巴嫩边境的以色列国防军部队。他们的快讯讲述了来自各种背景的以色列人的故事，他们的生活在三个月前发生了巨大的变化</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 19:48:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-08/ty-article/.highlight/reality-has-been-suspended-reporting-from-israels-front-lines-in-gaza-and-the-north/0000018c-e998-d249-a1ce-efddef3e0000</guid></item></channel></rss>